Author: Gateway#3763
Content:
[dscrd-hush] <Berg> We're in touch with them about reactivating HUSH.
Being a small alt-coin, we're low priority, and at the mercy of their schedule...
They intend to keep us listed and reactivate our trading, as things currently stand.
We can't provide a timeline, but note that it's entirely on Cryptopia to come through with this update, we provide support to them, but they work at their own pace and have their own priorities.
Much larger coins are still down on their site, they are making great progress, but we'll see when they get to us.
